name: Gözleme
description: While the butter slides, the tune comes in with steams and glide.  "Gözleme" is stuffed flatbread. It may have cheese, potatoes, spinach, ground beef, veggies, even honey-walnut if you prefer sweet. There's a similar dish in almost every cuisine like Indian, Afghanistan, Chinese etc.  Visual design by @blue-mbk (on twitter) hen.link/blue-mbk
